{"word":"H4723 - מִקְוֶה - miqveh - mik-veh' - Abiding - நிலைத்திருக்கும்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>מִקְוֶה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>miqveh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>mik-veh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Abiding / நிலைத்திருக்கும்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நம்பிக்கை. நம்புதல், சேர்ந்திருத்தல், குளங்கள், புடவைகள், நிலைத்திருத்தல் மிகுதி - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"hope, hope, ground of hope, things hoped for, outcome, collection, collected mass"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H6960 - קָוָה - qâvâh - kaw-vaw'/6960\">H6960</a>; something <i>waited</i> for, that is, <i>confidence</i> (objectively or subjectively); also a <i>collection</i>, that is, (of water) a <i>pond</i>, or (of men and horses) a <i>caravan</i> or <i>drove: - </i>abiding, gathering together, hope, linen yarn, plenty [of water], pool."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4721 - מַקְהֵל - maqhêl - mak-hale'/4721\">H4721</a>, <a href=\"#/H4722 - מַקְהֵלֹת - Maqhêlôth - mak-hay-loth'/4722\">H4722</a>, <a href=\"#/H4723 - מִקְוֶה - miqveh - mik-veh'/4723\">H4723</a>, <a href=\"#/H4724 - מִקְוָה - miqvâh - mik-vaw'/4724\">H4724</a>, <a href=\"#/H6950 - קָהַל - qâhal - 'kaw-hal'/6950\">H6950</a>, <a href=\"#/H6951 - קָהָל - qâhâl - kaw-hawl'/6951\">H6951</a>, <a href=\"#/H6952 - קְהִלָּה - qᵉhillâh - keh-hil-law'/6952\">H6952</a>, <a href=\"#/H6953 - קֹהֶלֶת - qôheleth - ko-heh'-leth/6953\">H6953</a>, <a href=\"#/H6954 - קְהֵלָתָה - Qᵉhêlâthâh - keh-hay-law'-thaw/6954\">H6954</a>, <a href=\"#/H6955 - קְהָת - Qᵉhâth - keh-hawth'/6955\">H6955</a>, <a href=\"#/H6956 - קֳהָתִי - Qŏhâthîy - ko-haw-thee'/6956\">H6956</a>, <a href=\"#/H6957 - קַו - qav - kav/6957\">H6957</a>, <a href=\"#/H6959 - קֹובַע - qôwbaʻ - ko'-bah or ko-bah'/6959\">H6959</a>, <a href=\"#/H6960 - קָוָה - qâvâh - kaw-vaw'/6960\">H6960</a>, <a href=\"#/H6961 - קָוֶה - qâveh - kaw-veh'/6961\">H6961</a>, <a href=\"#/H6978 - קַו־קַו - qav-qav - kav-kav'/6978\">H6978</a>, <a href=\"#/H7035 - קָלַהּ - qâlahh - kaw-lah'/7035\">H7035</a>, <a href=\"#/H8445 - תֹּוקַהַת - Tôwqahath - to-kah'-ath/8445\">H8445</a>, <a href=\"#/H8615 - תִּקְוָה - tiqvâh - tik-vaw'/8615\">H8615</a>, <a href=\"#/H8616 - תִּקְוָה - Tiqvâh - tik-vaw'/8616\">H8616</a>"}]}